# 🏨 Luxury Hotel Menu UI

A modern **animated restaurant & hotel menu website** built using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.

---

## ✨ Features

* 🍽️ 15 Indian dishes with real images
* 🎬 Smooth animations + 3D flip cards
* 🌙 Luxury **dark hotel theme UI**
* 🥦 Veg / 🍗 Non-Veg filter
* 💰 Price filter system
* 🛒 Add to Cart functionality
* 📱 Fully responsive design

---

## 🚀 Live Demo

👉 https://siddtiwari25.github.io/menu/

